    <para id="import-auto-id1169736598423">(a) 122 W</para><para id="import-auto-id1169737770764">(b) <m:math><m:semantics><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mtext>.</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mtext>10</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">×</m:mo><m:msup><m:mtext>10</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow><m:mspace width="0.25em"/><m:mtext> J</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:mrow><m:mrow/></m:mrow><m:annotation encoding="StarMath 5.0"> size 12{2 "." "09" times "10" rSup { size 8{6} } " J"} {}</m:annotation></m:semantics></m:math></para><para id="import-auto-id1169737909423">(c) Work done by the motor is <m:math><m:semantics><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mtext>.</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mtext>61</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">×</m:mo><m:msup><m:mtext>10</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mn>7</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow><m:mspace width="0.25em"/><m:mtext> J</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:mrow><m:mrow/></m:mrow><m:annotation encoding="StarMath 5.0"> size 12{1 "." "61" times "10" rSup { size 8{7} } " J"} {}</m:annotation></m:semantics></m:math> ;thus the motor produces 7.67 times the work done by the man</para></solution>
